{"type": "article", "id": 17168, "title": "圆桌", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-06T06:29:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000341UCvXYqr6HD9hzSmI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这张木质圆桌看上去像一个倒扣着的酒杯，是由混凝土底座和木质圆桌面组成。意大利的工作室 buratti architetti 想要找到一个足够柔和的外观，而混凝土的材质在创造柔和曲线的同时也能承担起足够的重量，在极简中似乎蕴藏了无限可能。此外，半球形的底座也近似一个花苞，与圆面桌构成有趣的对比和平衡。<a href=\"http://www.burattiarchitetti.it/en/product/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144317imtbHsGfEayCn3dz.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"452\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55256724\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144317N1wUVWH4LIudGbXR.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"676\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.82640587\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144318b5yQAPvjSc9BqN81.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"820\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.00244499\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144318ubhqx9M1ojVer2i3.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"590\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72127139\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}